{"tid":2424783,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"哈里王子大讚《王冠》比報道真實 望被Damian Lewis扮演","createTime":"2021-02-27T01:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T10:41:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4d7538f02f59eaade3e43cbb427b621f69894cb1","tid":2424783,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"哈里王子在前晚播出的《The Late Late Show》節目中，在開篷巴士上接受英國名嘴James Corden訪問，提及對劇集《王冠》的感想時表示：「他們不會扮成是新聞，這是虛構，亦是建基於真實，但當然不是嚴格的準確。我覺得看《王冠》舒服過看到關於家人、太太和我自己的新聞故事。那些故事很明顯是虛構，但卻報道成事實一樣。」哈里王子又認為劇集應該找男星Damian Lewis扮演他，而James亦搞笑地指他能扮演威廉王子。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210227/D2JHF36CHZC5LB7KSSTIDBRVMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210227%2FD2JHF36CHZC5LB7KSSTIDBRVMQ%2F&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2BwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=57d605f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210227%2FD2JHF36CHZC5LB7KSSTIDBRVMQ%2F&h=bb836031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210227/D2JHF36CHZC5LB7KSSTIDBRVMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"9e470aaee496e1b4d85d6724a71e65a685d242c0","tid":2424783,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T01:34:02.000Z","msg":"王子？"},{"pid":"e10313f3fba1cc69afe0526bdef7b6d70bf516ef","tid":2424783,"uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T02:23:37.000Z","msg":"attention seeking whore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96ad7b40acadb122cb743264d1733546123788b","tid":2424783,"uid":39492,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T02:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又係自己要脫離屋企束縛<br />\n依家就成撚日拎自己屋企嚟刷存在感"},{"pid":"06d8ad207551b4b4be6c7f0f57417596507d01d1","tid":2424783,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a96ad7b40acadb122cb74